                "reputation": 42071,
                "display_name": "Kevin Meredith",
                "accept_rate": 68
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1345575756,
            "creation_date": 1345575123,
            "body": "<p>My WAR failed to auto-explode after I dropped it into the /webapps/ directory in tomcat7 because of read-only file permissions.<\/p>\n\n<p>After I changed the .WAR file permissions, the WAR was exploded successfully.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 12061204,
            "question_id": 3208709,
            "last_edit_date": 1345575756
        }
